1
00:00:23,280 --> 00:00:25,600
No. Tawan, no.

2
00:00:25,920 --> 00:00:29,680
I'm sorry. I'm sorry if I offended you.

3
00:00:31,680 --> 00:00:33,800
But please don't leave again.

4
00:00:34,760 --> 00:00:38,840
I just wanted to terminate the contract,
not stop knowing you.

5
00:00:39,920 --> 00:00:41,360
I'm sorry.

6
00:00:43,720 --> 00:00:45,440
In the past eight years...

7
00:00:48,600 --> 00:00:52,400
In the past eight years without you
by my side, it's been so hard.

8
00:00:55,160 --> 00:00:56,880
Please don't leave again.

9
00:00:58,760 --> 00:01:01,880
♪ I was like a sun without rays of light ♪

10
00:01:01,880 --> 00:01:03,800
I'm sorry.

11
00:01:04,280 --> 00:01:07,520
♪ I never mattered ♪

12
00:01:07,520 --> 00:01:12,360
♪ With no one to rely on ♪

13
00:01:12,360 --> 00:01:17,800
♪ Until you came along and changed everything in me ♪

14
00:01:17,800 --> 00:01:21,120
♪ Helped me find true love ♪

15
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:25,800
♪ And realize who to live for ♪

16
00:01:26,440 --> 00:01:27,960
Don't cry.

17
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:31,400
♪ I'm now filled with your shadow ♪

18
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:33,320
Stop being a crybaby.

19
00:01:33,320 --> 00:01:35,400
♪ As the light to my heart ♪

20
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:36,920
I'm not going anywhere.

21
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:40,800
♪ You are the moon in my heart ♪

22
00:01:40,800 --> 00:01:42,160
Thank you very much.

23
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:48,160
♪ You make everything ♪

24
00:01:48,240 --> 00:01:52,520
♪ More meaningful every day ♪

25
00:01:52,520 --> 00:01:57,880
♪ I wanna be your sun ♪

26
00:01:57,880 --> 00:02:01,680
♪ Please let me ♪

27
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:06,840
♪ Be by your side and keep on loving you ♪

28
00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:24,120
Hungry? I could eat.

29
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:26,560
Shall we get something to eat?

30
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:32,440
Huh? Where is it?

31
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:36,960
I'm sure I put it here.

32
00:02:37,880 --> 00:02:40,480
If you're talking about the food in there,

33
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:42,840
I saw Typhoon take it with him.

34
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:46,760
He must have grabbed the wrong ones.

35
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:50,240
I'm so bummed. I ordered it for you.

36
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:57,320
There's nothing to eat now.

37
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:01,760
I'll order it for you again. Won't be long.

38
00:03:02,480 --> 00:03:03,360
Hey.

39
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:04,240
Huh?

40
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:05,280
No need.

41
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:08,760
I'll make us egg fried rice.

42
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:10,680
Egg fried rice?

43
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:18,640
Don't worry, Tawan. I'll make you my signature dish.

44
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:22,880
It will actually be edible, right?

45
00:03:23,720 --> 00:03:27,160
This dish won't implode my kitchen, I promise.

46
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:28,600
Sit down.

47
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:30,520
Okay.

48
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:33,880
The water's boiling.

49
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,280
Be careful. It's hot.

50
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:13,440
There.

51
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:16,440
I've been told you love noodles.

52
00:04:17,880 --> 00:04:18,880
Well...

53
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:21,600
I'm digging in.

54
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,960
Delicious.

55
00:04:42,520 --> 00:04:45,520
So there's officially one dish you can make.

56
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,040
Just like Mr. Thana.

57
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:53,560
He's the one who made sure I knew how to make this.

58
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:56,080
And he'd said exactly the same thing.

59
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:59,480
He said, "At least there's one dish you can make."

60
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,120
So good.

61
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:23,160
Oh, just a sec.

62
00:05:26,640 --> 00:05:27,840
Hello, boss.

63
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:31,000
Ayla, how are you doing?

64
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:35,000
I just found out after my flight landed.

65
00:05:35,400 --> 00:05:36,800
I almost went into shock.

66
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:40,160
Does Mr. Thana know?

67
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,840
Not yet, boss.

68
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:44,960
But please

69
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:48,800
don't tell him yet. I don't want him to worry.

70
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:50,360
I'll tell him myself later.

71
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:52,000
Okay.

72
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:55,200
We're looking through security footage

73
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:57,280
and coordinating with Ms. Rawee's team.

74
00:05:57,800 --> 00:06:00,160
This is outrageous. It's unacceptable.

75
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:04,040
I won't let this go.
I will get the people responsible to justice.

76
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:06,520
As for your work, you don't have to worry.

77
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:09,840
Take a break. I'll have Tik give you a new schedule.

78
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:12,160
Don't come in for a while.

79
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:15,120
Let me upgrade the entire security system here.

80
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:18,040
Okay? You understand, right?

81
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:19,760
I do, boss.

82
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:22,960
And how's Ms. Rawee doing?

83
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:26,680
She's okay now. Don't worry.

84
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:32,160
Tell her all the medial expenses will be taken care of.

85
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:34,600
Thank you very much, boss.

86
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,600
Take care of yourself, Ayla.

87
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:47,800
I guarantee you my boss is chewing out everyone
at the office right now.

88
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:56,840
How could you let this happen?

89
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,800
Did I not tell you

90
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:07,040
that the artists' safety must come first?

91
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:10,520
But you let this horrible thing happen to Ayla

92
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,760
in front of your own office building!

93
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:15,120
If you continue to be this careless

94
00:07:15,400 --> 00:07:19,440
and something like this happens to our other artists,

95
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,240
how will we face the public?

96
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:24,720
How will you tell their parents?

97
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:27,880
When we asked them for their permission,

98
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:31,320
we promised them we'd take good care of their kids.

99
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:34,240
Please keep that promise.

100
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:37,200
Otherwise,

101
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:39,640
let's just shut down this company!

102
00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:46,120
Don't blindly expect profits from the artists

103
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:50,280
if we haven't done our best to take care of them.

104
00:07:56,520 --> 00:08:00,760
So that means
you don't have to go into the office today?

105
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:04,760
After this fiasco,

106
00:08:04,960 --> 00:08:08,040
I expect to be taken off work for a few days.

107
00:08:38,400 --> 00:08:41,520
We're wondering if you're wavering a little

108
00:08:41,520 --> 00:08:42,840
Your secret's safe with us.

109
00:08:46,520 --> 00:08:48,040
I think you have to choose.

110
00:08:48,040 --> 00:08:49,760
Do you want to protect her

111
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:52,560
as a bodyguard protects her VIP,

112
00:08:52,560 --> 00:08:56,520
or do you want to protect
and take care of her as your life partner?

113
00:08:57,520 --> 00:08:59,480
Are you allowed to look at me differently

114
00:08:59,560 --> 00:09:03,040
where you're not my bodyguard
and I'm not your VIP?

115
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:05,600
I'm not a good option.

116
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:12,000
♪ The closer we are, the further it feels ♪

117
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:15,360
♪ Never once ♪

118
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:19,320
♪ Did you notice ♪

119
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:23,080
♪ What my heart was feeling ♪

120
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:26,880
♪ When I look at you, my eyes say it all ♪

121
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:31,960
♪ Waiting only for you to pay me attention ♪

122
00:09:32,040 --> 00:09:38,200
♪ My heart yells every day
But its voice never reaches you ♪

123
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:42,240
♪ I want you to know how long I've kept this in ♪

124
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:46,840
♪ Do you have any idea ♪

125
00:09:46,920 --> 00:09:49,560
♪ As each minute goes by ♪

126
00:09:49,560 --> 00:09:55,280
♪ How much my heart wants to say I love you? ♪

127
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:12,520
♪ When I look at you, my eyes say it all ♪

128
00:10:12,520 --> 00:10:17,120
♪ Do you have any idea ♪

129
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:19,840
♪ As each minute goes by ♪

130
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:26,200
♪ How much my heart wants to say I love you? ♪
